column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  GN.distance, p.petroR5#_r, SM.logMassFROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID  Join stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust as SM ON p.specObjID = SM.specObjIDWHERE  s.z between # and #ORDER BY distance
